  Chu2-au7 1740 ni5 goa2 kap peng5-iu2 Oe7-su-li2 hoat-seng liau2 chin-li2 kian3-kai2 siong7 e5 mou5-chhat. Oe7--si7 ti7 goa2 khi3 Bi2-kok liau2-au7 bo5 loa7-ku2, chiu7 kap Mou5-ni2-i5-a hiaN-ti7 (Morabians) toan7-choat8 ong2-lai5, khai-si2 thoan5-iong5 kiong5-liat8 e5 A-bi2-ni5-a to7-li2 (Arminian Doctrines), siong-sin3 chu7-iu5 i3-chi3 e5 soat, siang7-si5 i koh tek8-piat8 chu3-tiong7 tat8-kau3 bo5-choe7 e5 oan5-choan5 (Sinless Perfectiong). Chiah-e5 khoaN3-hoat kap goan2 tong-chhou sou2 leng2-siu7 e5 oan5-choan5 siong-hoan2. Goa2 (Hoai5-tek-hui) chhim-sin3 keng2-soan2 e5 to7-li2 (Doctrine of Election). Goa2 si7 an2-ni kong2: ¡§Chi2-u7 kam3-chhat jin5-sim e5 Chu2, hiau2-tit tui3 goa2 thoat-li7 se3-siok8 i2-au7, goa2 thang kiaN e5 sim-leng5 sou2 keng-lek8 e5 khou2-thang3. Choe7-ok e5 hoe5-ek8 hou7 goa2 kak-tit chin sit-taN2, goa2 mi5-jit8 eng7 bak8-sai2 choe3 png7 thun. Na7-si7 goa2 giong2-bong7 goa2 sou2 chhak8 e5 Chu2. (Chu2 e5 si2 si7 ui7 goa2). Goa2 siu7 un tit kiN3 I e5 un-tian2 che-si7 ho5-teng2 e5 chu7-iu5 kap hong-hu3, I e5 chu5-ai3 si7 ho5-teng2 bo5 han7 koh eng2-kiu2, tui3 an2-ni goa2 e5 sim tit-tioh8 an-ui3. Ah! Tui3 ti7 hiah e5 khak-sit8 tit-tioh8 eng3-un2 e5 leng5 e5! In3-ki3 e5 lang5, keng2-soan2 e5 un-hui7 kap eng2 tit po2-siu2 e5 to7-li2 si7 goa7-nih koan5 koh chhim! Goa2 chhim-chhim liah8-choe3 tu5-hui lang5 e7 siong-sin3 ji5-chhiaN2 ka-ki7 the2-hoe7 chiah-e5 tiong7-iau3 e5 chin-li2, i chiu7 boe7-oe7 thoat-li7 ka-ki7. Chi2-u7 chhim-sin3 chiah-e5 chin-li2, ji5-chhiaN2 khak-sit8 chai chaiN2-iuN7 lai5 eng3-iong7 ti7 ka-ki7 e5 sin-chiuN7, i chiah e7 sit8-heng5 ti7 sin3-sim e5 tiong-kan, bo5 ui7-tioh8 ka-ki7 lai5 oah8, lai5 oah8 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 KiaN2 e5 lai7-bin7. Si7 thiaN3 chhui-pek i khi3 sun7-hok8, peng7 m7-si7 tui3 kiaN-hiaN5 e5 sim. Lan2 ho5-pit tui-chhoe7 lai5 kiu5 ka-ki7 e5 gi7 the5-chhiong3 chu7-iu5 i3-chi3; lan2 i2-keng u7 chit8-e5 ho2 tit bo5 pi2 e5 gi7 thang hiong2-siu7, koh u7 Siong7-te3 beh chiong eng2-oan2 e5 eng5-iau3 ke-thiN hou7 lan2, chiau3 I sou2 hoaN-hi2 e5 ti7 lan2 e5 lai7-bin7 lip8-chi3 kiaN5 tai7-chi3. 
  Goa2 kiaN liau2 ui7-tioh8 chin-li2 siong7 kian3-kai2 e5 put-tong5, chiu7 hou7 hiaN-ti7 pun-khui. Sou2-i2 goa2 siuN7 chiah-e5 ti7 hiaN-ti7 tiong e5 hun-lih8, u7 si5 hou7 goa2 e5 sim chin tam-iu, na7-si7 bo5 kau3-giah8 hou7 goa2 kiaN-hiaN5 ki5-koai3. Cheng3 kau3-su be7-oe7 siuN7 siang7-khoan2 e5 su7, kong2 siang7-khoan2 e5 oe7, kiat-ko2 tong-jian5 si7 hun-lih8. Na7-si7 goan7 Siong7-te3 siuN2-su3 goan2, hou7 goan2 e7 pi2-chhu2 po2-chhi5 seng5-sit8 khun2-chhiat ji5-chhiaN2 pun be7-khui e5 thiaN3 sim, chu7-jian5 goan2 tak8-lang5 u7 ka-ki7 e5 i3-kian3. Ah! Goa2 ho5-teng2 him-bou7 thian-ka! Ti7 hia eng2-oan2 bo5 hun-lih8, ia7 bo5 u7 cheng-chip, tai7-ke chin7-lat8 chhiuN3-koa o-lo2 hit-ui7 che7 ti7 po2-cho7 teng2 e5 iuN5-ko. Goa2 chun2-pi7 lau5 thiaN3 e5 bak8-sai2, goa2 khoai3-lok8 goan7-i3 se2 jim7-ho5 hiaN-ti7 e5 kha. Chin--e5, goa2 goan7-i3 choe3 cheng3-lang5 e5 lou5-pok8. Chu2 sou2 ke-thiN hou7 goa2 e5 chun-kui3, it-hoat hou7 goa2 kam2-kak ka-ki7 put-phoe3. U7-si5 goa2 seN-khi2 iam3-ouN3 ka-ki7 e5 sim. 
  Keh-ni5 goa2 to3-lai5 Eng-kok, pun2 koat-teng7 beh giam5-siu2 tiong-lip8, na7-si7 khoan5-keng2 pek goa2 put tek-put tioh8 kong-khai soan-pou3 goa2 e5 sou2-sin3, peng7 hoan2-tui3 Oe7--si7 sou2 thoan5--e5. Ka-chai3 chit-khoan2 cheng5-keng2 bo5 ku2, goan2 nng7-lang5 chiu7 koh saN ho5-bok8. Goa2 bat sia2 phoe hou7 Oe7-su-li2 (Bi2-i2-bi2, a2-si7 kio3-choe3 Sun5-li2-hoe7 e5 khai-chou2) kong2, ¡§Goa2 sui-jian5 chu2-tiuN tek8-piat8 e5 keng2-soan2, tan7-si7 goa2 chiong Ia5-sou peh8-peh8 sang3 hou7 tak8-e5 lang5. Chhut-chai7 li2 chiong seng3-kiat chu2-tiuN kau3 goa7-nih8 kek8-toan, goa2 chong2-si7 be7 thang tong5-i3 lang5 iau2 oah8 ti7 se3-kan e5 si5, lai7-bin7 e5 choe7-seng3 oe7 thang oan5-choan5 siau-biat8. Tan7-si7 goan7 sou2-u7 e5 cheng-pian7 long2-chong2 theng5-chi2. Hou7 lan2 bo5 kong2 pat8-hang7, chi2-u7 thoan5 Ia5-sou Ki-tok kap I teng3 sip8-ji7-ke3. Che-si7 goa2 e5 koat-sim. Goan7 Chu2 kap li2 e5 leng5 tong5-chai7.¡¨ 
  U7 lang5 khou2-khng3 goa2 ka-ki7 siat kau3-phai3, na7-si7 goa2 kian-koat hoan2-tui3 chit-hang7 su7. Goa2 bat sia2-phoe hou7 goa2 e5 peng5-iu2 lai5 piau2-beng5 goa2 e5 sim-chi3 kong2: ¡§Li2 e5 koan-chhat si7 cheng3-khak e5, goa2 m7-goan7 seng5-lip8 chong-phai3, ia7 m7-goan7-i3 ka-ki7 choe3 leng2-siu3. Bo5, goa2 goan7 lang5 e5 mia5, chong-phai3, kap kong-hoe7 long2 sit-pai7; chi2-u7 Ia5-sou Ki-tok si7 it-chhe3, koh si7 chhiong-moa2 it-chhe3! Goa2 siu7 koe3 kau3-giah8 che7 e5 iong3-hou7 chhui-chun, hou7 goa2 kam2-kak thou2-khui3 hui3-khi3. Na7 m7-si7 goa2 hit ui7 thang chheng-hou o-lo2 e5 Chu2 e5 li7-ek, I ai3 goa2 ti7 kun5-chiong3 e5 tiong-kan chhut-hian7, se3-kai3 kim-au7 oh-tit koh thiaN-kiN3 goa2 e5 tai7-chi3 lah.¡¨ 
  ¡§Ku7-lang5 si7 ho5-teng2 e5 m7-kam teng3-si2 ti7 sip8-ji7-ke3 teng2, chiu7-si7 i2-keng kiok8-pou7 oaN7-sin e5 sim-su ia7 lan5-tit kang3-loh8 khiam-pi, thoat-li7 chu7-su kap phian-kian3. Lang5 hong3-khi3 koan5-ui7, si7 chap8-hun e5 kou-put-chiong, chi7-chui7 goan7 ti7 kau3-hoe7 kap se3-kai3 e5 bak8-chiu cheng5 kang3 ke7, pi2 choe3 se3 e5 iau2-khah se3. 
  Chong2-si7 che-si7 Ia5-sou e5 kian3-cheng3-jin5 sou2 tek-khak tioh8 hak8-sip8 e5 hak8-kho3. Ah! Goa2 chi2-u7 oh8 chit8-e5 khi2-thau5 na7-tiaN7. Goa2 kam2-kak chu7-iu5, bo5 u7 ka-ki7 e5 ke3-oe7, bo5 sou2 ki5-kiu5, bo5 sou2 ai-oan3; na7-si7 goa2 siong-sin3 ka-ki7 u7 chit8 tui3 tan-sun5 e5 bak8-chiu, chi2-u7 kiu5 kiu3-un e5 khong3-khoah soan-thoan5, chit8-sut-a2 to bo5 ui7-tioh8 ka-ki7 siat-lip8 kau3-hoe7 kap kau3-phai3 e5 i3-su3. Che-si7 goa2 e5 sim chhim-chhim kiaN-ui3 e5. Chi2-u7 chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni, goa2 tit liau2 peng5-an, chit e5 peng5-an si7 se3-kan-lang5 sou2 m7-chai--e5, si7 cheng-koan5 toat8-li7 e5 lang5 sou2 m7-bat--e5. Hou7 lang5 pai5-thek, siu7 lang5 biau2-si7, chek-pi7 kap hui2-pong3, chiah-e5 tui3 goa2 si7 iu2-ek. Goa2 choe3 chhin-bit8 e5 peng5-iu2 phoe-pheng5 goa2, kap goa2 hun-lih8, hoan2-tng2 hou7 goa2 chhoe7 kau3 hit ui7 peng5-iu2 tiong e5 peng5-iu2 e5 chin7-tiong seng5-sit8. In-ui7 chit-e5 goa2 siu7-liau2 ka3-si7, un2-khng3 ka-ki7 ti7 eng5-iau7 I2-ma2-loe7-li7 eng2-oan2 kong-gi7 e5 lai7-bin7, chap8-hun ti-chiok, in-ui7 chai-iaN2 lang5 e5 sim kap i3-su3 e5 Chu2 hian7-chai7 khoaN3-kiN3 goa2 e5 sim-liam7, chiong-lai5 iau2-ku2 beh ti7 cheng3-lang5 e5 bin7-cheng5 piau2-pek8 goa2 sim-tiong e5 cheng3-tit8.¡¨ (i2-siong7 si7 Hoai5-tek-hui sian-siN sia2 hou7 peng5-iu2 e5 phoe-tiong e5 oe7). 
