  Peng5-iu2 in ti7 Bou7-ni2-hui (Moorfild) tah chit8-e5 toa7 pou3-peN5 ti7 hia kang2-to7. Chu2-au7 1742 ni5 Seng3-leng5 kang3-lim5 cheh e5 chiu-ni5 ki3-liam7-jit8, goa2 chhai2-chhu2 chit8-e5 ho2-taN2 e5 heng5-tong7. Hit sou2-chai7 u7 chit8 e5 toa7 kong2-tiuN5, mui2-pai2 tu2-tioh8 cheh-jit8, choan5-tiuN5 chhiong-moa2 chap8-hoe3-thoaN, u7 chau2 kang-ou5--e5, pian3 pa2-hi3--e5, choe3 ka-le2-ang-a2-hi3--e5, chiu7-si7 chap8 hoe gou7-sek long2 chiau5-chng5. Ti7 hit chit8 pai2 goa2 kap kui2-na7 ui7 hiaN-ti7 ti7 hit cha2-khi2 e5 6 tiam2 chiu7 chhut-hoat, ti7 kong2-tiuN5-siong7 keng2 chit8-ui7 tu2 ho2 e5 sou2-chai7, choe3 goan2 ia2-goa7 pou3-to7 e5 kang2-tai5. Chheng-cha2 i2-keng u7 chit8-ban7-goa7 lang5 chu7-chip8 ti7 hia. Goa2 peh-chiuN7 ia2-goa7 e5 kang2-tai5, sim-lai7 kam2-kak chin hoaN-hi2, in-ui7 khoaN3--lai5 chit pai2 goa2 si7 i2-keng chiam3 hong-thau5, pi2 mou5-kui2 tai7-seng he7-chhiu2 kang-chok. Lang5 liam-piN chau2 oa2-lai5 ui5 goa2, goa2 chiu7 eng7 ¡§Mou5-se ti7 khong3-ia2 chaiN2-iuN7 ku2-khi2 choa5, Jin5-chu2 ia7 tek-khak chiau3 an2-ni siu7 ku2-khi2¡¨ e5 oe7 ng3-theng3-chiong3 khai-kang2. Choan5-the2 siok-cheng7, in chu3-bak8 khoaN3 goa2, in chu3-sin5 teh thiaN, kau3-boe2 in thi5-khau3 lah. Goa2 tit-tioh8 kou2-le7, e7-pou koh chhut-hoat. Na7-si7 kong-keng2 toa7 pian3 lah, hian7-chai7 kiuh-kiuh-jiong2 hoa7-hoa7-hau2 chin hun7-chap8 chin jiau2-loan7. Phah-kou2--e5, pun5-chhoe--e5, sio2-thiu2-a2, choe3 ka-le2-ang-a2-hi3--e5, tian2-lam2 ia2-siu3--e5, kap ki5-thaN e5 hi3 bo5-ki5 put-iu2, khip-in2 kui-kun5 e5 lang5 tai7-iok u7 nng7-ban7 goa7 lang5. Chin-chiaN3 si7 chhan5-nih8 e5 ngou2-kok i2-keng sek8-lah, thang siu-koah lah, kho2-sioh siu-koah kui Piat8-se-pok, m7-si7 kui hou7 kiu3-siok8 e5 Chu2. 
  Goa2 e5 kang2-tai5 siat ti7 tui3-bin7, khoaN3 khi2--lai5 ho2 chhin-chhiuN7 Po2-lo5 sou2 kong2 chit8-iuN7, siu7 tiau3 lai5 kap I2-hut-sou2 e5 ia2-siu3 chian3-tou3, in-ui7 an2-ni goa2 chiu7 tui3 in toa7-siaN kong2 ¡§Toa7 ah! I2-hut-sou2 e5 A-ti2-bi2¡¨. Choe3 pa2-hi3 e5 lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 kun5-chiong3 li7-khui in, choan2-ng3 tui3 pou3-to7 e5 lang5, chiu7 toa7 siu7-khi3, chiu7 khui-siaN soan-jiong2 chha2-nau7, au7-lai5 chiu7 tui3 goan2 tim3 chhau3-nng7, chioh8-thau5 kap si2-niau. Goan2 chit8-si5 chhin-chhiuN7 seng-khu siu7 pau-ui5 ti7 beng2-sai e5 tiong-kan, na7-si7 toa7 pou7-hun7 e5 theng3-chiong3 iu5-goan5 ke3-siok8 koh chiap-soa3 teh thiaN. Kau3 kiat-sok e5 si5, goa2 koh soan-pou3 kim-am3 beh koh ti7 chia siang7 chit e5 te7-tiam2 koh kang2-ian2. 
  Tng goa2 koh kau3 kong2-tiuN5 e5 si5, goa2 tit-tioh8 chin toa7 e5 kou2-le7, khoaN3-kiN3 i2-keng u7 kui2-na7-chheng ti7 hia teh theng3-hau7, chong2-si7 goa2 u7 gu7-tioh8 koh-khah u7 chou-chit e5 hoan2-khong3. Tui3 kang2-tai5 e5 chiaN3-bin7, u7 chit8 e5 Sat-tan3 e5 thau5-chhiu2 phah-chhiu2, ti7 toa7-hi3-tai5 teng2 ng3 kun5-chiong3 hian3 i thiam2-mi7-lang5 e5 khoe-hai5. Na7-si7 tng in khoaN3-kiN3 goa2 chheng7 ou-phau3 bok8-su-hok8 chiuN7 kang2-tai5 e5 si5, i chiu7 li7-khui i e5 hi3, chau2 koe3-lai5. An2-ni Sat-tan3 toa7 hoat i e5 koan5-ui, lim2 goa2 be7 tiau5 e5 khoan2, tui3 an2-ni hit e5 sio2-thiu2-a2 chiu7 giah8 chit8-ki tng5-tng5 e5 piN, chau2 oa2--lai5, au7-bin7 toe3 chit8-tin7 siu7-khi3 moa2-moa2 bo5 ui7 thang thau2-khui3 chin sit-i3 e5 choe3-hi3-a2. Chit8 e5 gau5 chhia-pun3-tau2 e5 sio2-thiu2 chiu7 khia5 ti7 tang5-phoaN7 e5 keng-thau5-teng2, eng7 piN phah goa2, ji5-chhiaN2 chng-choe3 siuN chhut-lat8 soa3 tui3 keng-thau5-teng2 siak-loh8--lai5. Au7-lai5 in koh thiau-so chit8 e5 bou7-chip8 peng e5 kun-cho5 phah-kou2 lai5 keng-koe3 kun5-chiong3. Goa2 khoaN3-kiN3 in ti7 thau5-cheng5 tui3-bin7 teh lai5, goa2 chiu7 chhiaN2 kun5-chiong3 poah-khui chit8 tiau5 lou7, tai7-ke pai5 choe3 nng7-peng5, kun-cho5 tiam7-tiam7 kiaN5 koe3-khi3, kun5-chiong3 chiah koh hap8-oa2. In sou2-u7 e5 kiau2-jiau2 long2 sit-pai7, chiu7 chu7-chip8 kui kun5, eng7 tek-ko pak8 ki5 ng3 theng3-chiong3 e5 ui7 lai5, na7-si7 kiaN5-oa2 lai5 chhun kui2-na7 chhioh chiu7 kau3-ui7 e5 si5, hut-jian5 in e5 loe7-pou7 hoat-seng cheng-chip ka-ki7 loan7, chiu7 hiat-kak8 ki5, oat8-tng2-sin to5-chau2. Tui3 an2-ni goa2 chiah tit-tioh8 an-cheng7 pou3-to7. Goan2 to3-lai5 kau3 pou3-piN5, goa2 siang-peng5 e5 te7-a2-lai7 te2 moa2 hiah e5 siu7 kam2-tong7 ui7-tioh8 ka-ki7 e5 leng5-hun5 tioh8-kip e5 lang5 sou2 sia2 e5 choa2-toaN-a2, goa2 ti7 kui2-na7-chheng lang5 hoaN-hi2 au5-kio3 o-lo2 Chu2 e5 tiong-kan sui5-tiuN sui5-tiuN thak8 hou7 tai7-ke thiaN. Keh-jit8 goa2 siu7 chhiaN2 kau3 ti7 Ma2-li7-lai5-pho e5 toa7 chhau2-pou (Marylebone Fields), ti7 hia si7 phah kun5-thau5, kap keng3-ki e5 lang5 sou2 chu7-chip8 e5 sou2-chai7. Goa2 khoaN3-kiN3 u7 che7-che7 lang5 chu7-chip8, chiu7 eng7 ¡§Goa2 bo5 liah8 hok-im choe3 kian3-siau3, che hok-im pun2 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 toa7 koan5-leng5, beh kiu3 it-chhe3 siong-sin3 e5 lang5¡¨ (Lo5-ma2 1:16). 
  Goa2 sou2 khia7 e5 kang2-tai5 si7 chap8-hun bo5 chai7, mui2-pai2 kiaN5 tin2-tang7 e5 si5, io5-io5 pai2-pai2 lok8-lok8-hian2 beh peng2-koe3 e5 khoan2. Tui3-tek8 khoaN3-chhut chit e5 gui5-hiam2 chiu7 thiau-ti5 e-kheh kin7 kang2-tai5 e5 lang5, kai-chai3 goa2 long2 bo5 siu7 hai7. Tng goa2 li7-khui kang2-tai5, kiaN5 ng3 be2-chhia e5 si5, kak-tit au7-bin7 u7 lang5 eng7 sim2-mih8 lai5 khap8-tioh8 goa2 e5 bo7-a2 kap thau5-mng5 e5 khoan2-sit, goa2 kin2 oat8-thau5 koe3-lai5 khoaN3, chiah chai tui3-bin7 u7 chit8 e5 lang5 chhiu2 giah8 kiam3, i e5 kiam3-boe2 tu2-tu2 tui3 goa2 e5 pin3-piN chhak8--lai5. Kai-chai3 u7 pat8-lang5 khoaN3-kiN3, eng7 koaiN2-a2 phah ka-lauh8 hit ki kiam3. Kun5-chiong3 khoaN3 hit e5 khoan2-sit toa7 siu7-khi3, chiu7 kui-kun5 khi2-lai5 kong-kek hit e5 giah8-kiam3 e5 lang5, siat-su2 na7 m7-si7 goa2 e5 peng5-iu2 kiu5-cheng5, hit e5 lang5 khiong2-kiaN e7 siu7 cheng3-lang5 phah chin thiam2. 
  Goa2 chit8 sut-a2 to bo5 lun2-neh sit-taN2, keh-jit8 koh khi3 hit e5 goan5-ui7. Tui3-tek8 koh lai5 soan-jiong2, khiong2-hek, na7-si7 long2 bo5 kong-hau7. U7 chit8 e5 lang5 pi2 pat8-lang5 koh-khah hiong5-ok, peh-chiuN7 oa2-kin7 kang2-tai5 e5 chhiu7-a2, choe3-chhut phaiN2-khoaN3 e5 heng5-hai5. Khi2-thau5 goa2 bo5 tiuN-ti5 tioh8 chit8-kiaN, goa2 siuN7 sat-tan3 hian7-chai7 bi7-bian2 thai3-koe3-thau5 lah. Kau3 goa2 sim an-tiaN7 e5 si5, goa2 chiu7 khou2-khng3 cheng3-lang5 kong2, lin2 ki3-jian5 chhin-bak8 khoaN3-kiN3 chit-khoan2 e5 cheng5-heng5, chiu7 e7 chu7-toan3 goa2 tui3 ti7 lang5 e5 phoaN3-toan3 hit e5 oe7 si7 chho3-gou7 a2 m7-si7. Chiau3-tioh8 keng3-khian5 e5 Hok-ni2 Chu2-kau3 (Bishop Hall) e5 oe7 kong2, ¡§Chhut-chai7 lang5 ka-ki7 e5 si5, lang5 si7 poaN3 kui2 poaN3 khim5-siu3,¡¨ tui3 an2-ni choan5-tiuN5 tiong5-sin siok-cheng7. Goa2 jiat8-seng5 khoan3-bian2 in, jian5-au7 kap goa2 e5 tang5-phoaN7 to3-lai5 pou3-piN5. Goan2 chiu7 ti7 hia lai5 long2 thak8 sia2 hou7 goa2 e5 choa2-toaN, lai5 kiat-sok chit e5 cheh-jit8 e5 kang-chok, kui2-na7 chheng lang5 chu7-hoe7 o-lo2 kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3. 
  Goa2 ti7 chia beh tek8-piat8 the5-khi2 chit8-hang7 kek8 chhu3-bi7 e5 su7. Chiu7-si7 tng-ti7 goa2 teh kang2-ian2 e5 si5, tak8-pai2 u7 chin-che7 gin2-na2 hoaN-hi2 ui5-ui5 lai5 che7 ti7 tai5-a2 e5 kia7-a2-teng2, pang-chan7 theh8 theng3-chiong3 e5 choa2-tiau5-a2. In tng ti7 kiau2-jiau2 hoah-hiam3 e5 tiong-kan in chiong5-lai5 long2 m7-bat piau2-si7 kiaN-hiaN5 beh chau2. Mui2-pai2 goa2 siu7 phah e5 si5, in long2 giah8-khi2 lau5 bak8-sai2 se3-se3 e5 bak8-chiu khoaN3 goa2, na2 chhin-chhiuN7 in ng3-bang7 e7-tit thoe3 goa2 hou7 lang5 phah. Chit-pai2 e5 pou3-to7 tit-tioh8 350 goa7 lang5 hoan2-hoe2. 
