  Hoai5-tek-hui sian-siN si7 kin7-tai7 siang7 tai7-seng chhai2-eng7 ia2-goa7 thoan5-to7 e5 lang5, i eng7 lou7-thian pou3-to7 lai5 kiat-sok i e5 kang-chok, sit8-chai7 si7 chin tu2-ho2. Chhin-bak8 khoaN3-tioh8 i hit-jit8 e5 cheng5-heng5 e5 lang5 kian3-cheng3 kong2: ¡§I tui3 cho7-sek khi2-lai5 khia7 e5 si5. I e5 bin7-mau7 i2-keng si7 chit8-phiN kek8 u7 leng5-lek8 e5 to7-li2. I e5 bin7-mau7 chiau-chui7, bin7-sek chheN-peh8, hian2-si7 thiN-teng2 e5 kng ti7 i soe-lam2 e5 sin-the2-nih8 hoat-chhut. Chiah-e5 kam2-tong7 lang5 kek8-chhim. Sim-leng5 sui-jian5 goan7-i3, na7-si7 jiok8-the2 i2-keng tong3-be7-tiau5. I khia7 khi2-lai5 tiam7-tiam7 kui2-na7 hun-cheng ku2 bo5 kong2-oe7. Au7-lai5 chiah khui-chhui3 kong2: ¡§Goa2 chiaN3-chiaN3 si7 theng3-hau7 Siong7-te3 e5 si-un pang-chan7, in-ui7 goa2 chhim-chai I beh koh chit8-pai2 hu5-chhi5 goa2, hou7 goa2 e7 hong7 I e5 mia5 kong2-oe7.¡¨ I ko2-jian5 thoan5-chhut chit8-phiN kek8-ho2 e5 siau-sit (soat-kau3). Hit e5 soa3-boe2 tai7-khai3 si7 kong2 an2-ni: ¡§Goa2 (chi2 Hoai5-tek-hui pun2-sin) beh khi3 lah, beh khi3 hiong2-siu7 chit8 ui7 i2-keng u7-pi7 liau2 ho2 e5 an-hioh; Goa2 e5 jit8-thau5 i2-keng chiuN7-khi2--lai5, tui3 thiN phou2-chio3 che7-che7 lang5, hian7-chai7 khoai3 beh loh8 lah,....m7-si7, eng2-oan2 be7-e7 an2-ni, si7 tian-to3 khoai3 beh seng-koan5 kau3 be7 hui2-hoai7 eng5-iau7 e5 kek8-koan5. Goa2 pi2 che7-che7 lang5 ti7 te7-chiuN7 oah8 khah ku2,......Goa2 e5 jiok8-the2 sui-jian5 soe-lam2, na7-si7 goa2 e5 leng5 khiok si7 iong2-chong3. Goa2 ho5-teng2 goan7-i3 eng2-oan2 oah8 teh lai5 thoan5-iong5 Ki-tok, tan7-si7 goa2 khi3, si7 kap I tong5-chai7. Goa2 e5 it-seng si7 ho5-teng2 e5 te2 koh chiam7-si5, kap pai5 ti7 goa2 bak8-cheng5 toa7 ji5-chhiaN2 boe7 oan5-seng5 kang-chok pi2-kau3 khi2-lai5, chin-si7 toan2-chhiok, na7-si7 goa2 it-tan3 li7-khui se3-kan, peng5-an e5 Siong7-te3 tek-khak beh koan3-kou3 lin2, in-ui7 kin-a2-jit8 koan-sim siok8 thiN-teng2 e5 su7 e5 lang5 si7 ho5-teng2 e5 hi-han2.¡¨ 
  Ti7 hit-am3 toa7-khui3 chhoan2 e5 peN7 koh hoat, hou-khip kan-lan5. Keh cha2-khi2 6 tiam2 chiu7 li7-khui se3-kan to3-khi3 thiN-nih8. Si7 ti7 Chu2-au7 1770 ni5 9 geh8 30 jit8, hiong2-siu7 56 hoe3. 
