  Hoai5-tek-hui si7 tui3 Su3-tou5 i2-au7 kau3-taN lan5 tit u7 e5 toa7 thoan5-to7-chia2. Kham-tit chheng choe3 ¡§chit8-ki jiat8-liat8 chhan3-lan7 e5 hoe2-pe2¡¨ ti7 18 se3-ki2 e5 Eng-kok siok8-leng5 e5 su7 chin-ke7 chin tui7-loh8. Na7-si7 kin7-kin7 ti7 i choe3-kang e5 30 goa7 ni5 ku2, chiu7 chiong kok lai7 siok8-leng5 e5 cheng5-heng5 toa7 pian3, heng-khi2 toa7-kng lai5 pian3-chio3 chit e5 ou-am3 e5 si5-tai7, ban2-kiu3 liau2 Eng-kok e5 un7-mia7. I piaN3-mia7 choe3-kang, m7-kaN2 chit8-bak8 nih ku2 lai5 be7-ki3-tit Siong7-te3 kau-tai3 seng3 e5 chit. I ti7 kui2 le2-pai3 ku2 e5 sou2 choe3, chiu7 pi2 pat8-lang5 chit8-ni5 e5 sou2-choe3 khah che7, 30 goa7 ni5 ku2 m7-kaN2 chit8-jit8 pin5-toaN7. Che7-che7 ni5 ku2 siong5-siong5 mui2 le2-pai3 hiong3 kui2-na7-chheng e5 theng3-chiong3 lai5 kong2 to7-li2 tui3 40 tiam2-cheng kau3 60 tiam2-cheng e5 ku2. Kang-chok au7 bo5 hioh-khun3, ti7 chhu3-nih8 ke3-siok8 ki5-to2, thoe3 lang5 kiu5, a2-si7 gim5-si thak8-keng, che7-che7 lang5 tui3 i lai5 peh8-peh8 tit-tioh8 hok-im. Bok8-koai3 lang5 o-lo2 i kong2 ¡§Chai5-tek e5 lam5-chu2 che7-che7, na7-si7 tok8-tok8 li2 iaN5-koe3 it-chhe3.¡¨ TaN i leng5-lek8 e5 pi3-koat chai7 ti7 to2-ui7? Chiu7-si7 chai7 ti7 jiat8-ai3 leng5-hun5. Tng i ng3 choe7-jin5 kong2-oe7 e5 si5, i siong5-siong5 lau5 bak8-sai2. I e5 thi5-khau3 kam2-tong7 lang5 chin chhim, chio2-chio2 lang5 hoan2-khong3. I kong2 ¡§Lin2 chek-pi7 goa2 siong5-siong5 khau3, na7-si7 goa2 chaiN2-iuN7 e7 tit kim3-chi2 bo5 khau3 nih8? Lin2 be7 si2 e5 leng5-hun5 i2-keng ti7 hui2-biat8 e5 lip8-kiN5, na7-si7 lin2 ka-ki7 m7-chai thang ai-chham2 thi5-khau3. Lin2 tioh8 chai lin2 kho2-leng5 chiu7-si7 thiaN choe3-au7 chit8-phiN e5 to7-li2, i2-au7 koh bo5 u7 ki-hoe7 thang chiap-siu7 Ki-tok lah!¡¨ 
  Bi2-i2-bi2 hoe7 (Sun5-li2-hoe7) e5 Oe7-su-li2 Iok-han7 kian3-cheng3 kong2 ¡§Sou2 su3 e5 Seng3-leng5 chiong Siong7-te3 e5 thiaN3 koan3-ak ti7 i e5 sim, hou7 i tui3 lang5 moa2-moa2 u7 un-jiu5 ho5-peng5 bo5 phian-su e5 thiaN3. Tui3 chit e5 chheng3-chhut oang-oang lau5 e5 khau2-chai5, lau5 kau3 theng3-chiong3 e5 sim-pang5, ti3-kau3 hou7 tai7-ke toa7 siu7 kam2-tong7, hou7 ngi7-sim e5 choe7-jin5 oh-tit ti2-khong3. Chit e5 thiaN3-sim si5-siong5 hou7 i e5 thau5-khak chhin-chhiuN7 chui2-ti5, bak8-chiu na2-chun2 bak8-sai2 e5 chui2-choaN5.¡¨ 
